project1.title: Mood Match
project1.description: MoodMatch is a web application that helps users discover music playlists based on their mood and provides information about venues related to the artists in the playlist.

project2.title: Weather Dashboard
project2.description: A web app written in javascript, HTML and CSS that displays today's weather and a 5-day forecast (showing every 3 hours) for a city of the user's choice.

project3.title: Daily Planner
project3.description: A calendar application that allows a user to save events for each hour of the day.

project4.title: Code Quiz
project4.description: A web app written in javascript, HTML and CSS that displays a coding quiz and allows the user to record their highscore.

project5.title: Password Generator
project5.description: A javascript app that generates a password based on user input.

project6.title: Horiseon Web Services
project6.description: This project altered the HTML of an existing site to increase its SEO performance through use of semantic attributes.
